36
00:13:05,487 --> 00:13:07,186
Ostali su rekli da je poseban.

37
00:13:08,521 --> 00:13:09,986
I više od posebnog.

38
00:13:15,587 --> 00:13:17,186
Te oči vide sve.

39
00:13:20,321 --> 00:13:22,253
Kada se rodi dete, pravedni

40
00:13:22,254 --> 00:13:24,786
vođa će ustati da zauvek promeni
naše svet.

41
00:13:27,421 --> 00:13:32,353
To rođenje donosi promene.

42
00:13:34,754 --> 00:13:35,320
Bio si dobar.

43
